      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Well, after that shutdown in Bowling Green, the factory opened and reportedly has been running at “full production capacity” since. That apparently means two shifts working hard to bring you a mid-engine American sports car.",
