        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Demand for the C8 Corvette has been intense since it launched for the 2020 model year. It seems like everyone wants to get their hands on the car, which has led some to flip theirs for big bucks. And while orders for the 2021 model year have been officially closed for a while now, dealers have been taking orders for 2022 Chevrolet Corvettes since July 1.",
